{
  "id": "ex_technical_89ba2c34",
  "intent": "Execute PCR2 plate setup by transferring 2\u00b5L barcodes from reverse primer plates to PCR2 plates across all columns using P10 multichannel pipette. For plasma samples, transfer 10\u00b5L PCR1 products directly; for other sample types, perform consolidation transfers of 8\u00b5L water plus 2\u00b5L PCR1 product per well. Complete setup by adding 13\u00b5L total PCR2 master mix (6.5\u00b5L twice from top then bottom) to each column with 4x mixing at 10\u00b5L volume. Protocol supports 1-2 plate batches with tip replenishment pause between plates.",
